text: Hwylc is hæleþa þæs horsc ond þæs hygecræftig þæt þæt mæge asecgan, hwa mec on sið wræce, þonne ic astige strong, stundum reþe, þrymful þunie, þragum wræce fere geond foldan, folcsalo bærne, ræced reafige?

Hlin bið on eorþan, wælcwealm wera, þonne ic wudu hrere, bearwas bledhwate, beamas fylle, holme gehrefed, <heahum> meahtum <wrecen> on waþe, wide sended; hæbbe me on hrycge þæt ær hadas wreah foldbuendra, flæsc ond gæstas, somod on sunde.
Saga hwa mec þecce, oþþe hu ic hatte, þe þa hlæst bere.
